/coinflip/create\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mreturns 401 with missing JWT\u001b[90m 6\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[31m\u001b[39m\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m   \u001b[31m×\u001b[31m HTTP endpoint tests\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mPOST /coinflip/create\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mreturns 401 with expired JWT\u001b[90m 4\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[31m\u001b[39m\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m   \u001b[31m×\u001b[31m HTTP endpoint tests\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mPOST /coinflip/create\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mreturns 403 when body wallet mismatches JWT wallet\u001b[90m 4\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[31m\u001b[39m\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m   \u001b[31m×\u001b[31m HTTP endpoint tests\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mPOST /coinflip/create\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mreturns 409 with duplicate PDA (match ID collision)\u001b[90m 4\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[31m\u001b[39m\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m   \u001b[31m×\u001b[31m HTTP endpoint tests\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mPOST /coinflip/create\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mreturns 429 when rate limit exceeded\u001b[90m 3\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[31m\u001b[39m\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m   \u001b[31m×\u001b[31m HTTP endpoint tests\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mPOST /lord/create\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mreturns 200 with valid JWT\u001b[90m 3\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[31m\u001b[39m\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m   \u001b[31m×\u001b[31m HTTP endpoint tests\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mGET /rounds/:pda\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mreturns 200 for known PDA\u001b[90m 3\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[31m\u001b[39m\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m   \u001b[31m×\u001b[31m HTTP endpoint tests\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mGET /rounds/:pda\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mreturns 404 for unknown PDA\u001b[90m 3\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[31m\u001b[39m\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m   \u001b[31m×\u001b[31m HTTP endpoint tests\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mGET /health\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mreturns 200 with expected fields\u001b[90m 7\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[31m\u001b[39m\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m   \u001b[31m×\u001